CollectionNotes: Large mating lek of 100+ unknown hymenopteran males flying in formations along 50 meter long by 3 meter wide sandy patch alongside dirt road with 15+ females of Dasymutilla gloriosa running around examining holes in the same area. All were collected except the female bembicine host.
